item.description: Privacy Policy Your privacy is important to us. This extension does not collect, store, or transmit any personal or sensitive user data. We do not track your browsing activity, capture any information, or share data with third parties. If you have any questions or concerns regarding your privacy while using our extension, feel free to contact us. Modifications to Web Content This extension modifies HTML content on GitHub issues, pull request, and saved replies web pages to enhance your browsing experience.
